Program: aisearch

Date: 20 Mar 2024

Program purpose: Create an AI search engine.  This is effectively a front end 
for the Perplexity.ai API.

Languages used: JavaScript, HTML, Bootstrap, and CSS.

Setup: 
0. npm install --save-dev parcel
1.  npm init -y
2.  Edit package.json
3.  npm install
4.  create a src/index.html
5.  cd/src
6.  npm start    

parcel will run a local server with hot reloading.
localhost:1234
For more information on parcel, see https://parceljs.org/getting-started/webapp/